      <h1>Photography Websites with a Brain</h1>
      <div class="sub_header">
       Professionals use PhotoDeck for Portfolios, Secure Proofing and e-Commerce websites.
      </div>
     </div>
     <div class="clear"></div>
    </div>
   </div>
   <div class="grid_wrapper">
    <div class="grid_6_enh_2"> 
     <img src="http://w3assets.photodeck.com/wp-content/uploads/homepage/steve_wright.jpg" alt="Steve Wright" class="testimonial_image">
    </div>
    <div class="grid_6_enh_4">
     <p class="testimonial-quote main_testimonial"><big><b>“</b></big> The response from clients and contacts has been extremely positive. I could not be happier with what I’ve been able to achieve so far.</p>
